										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Instagram Story Highlights is one of the most popular features Instagram offers. <a href="https://business.instagram.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Over 500 million</a> accounts use it every day.</p>
<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Instagram-highlights-nextdoor-1.jpg" alt="Instagram Highlights - nextdoor instagram profile" width="416" height="600" class="aligncenter wp-image-76760 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Instagram-highlights-nextdoor-1.jpg 416w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/Instagram-highlights-nextdoor-1-208x300.jpg 208w" sizes="(max-width: 416px) 100vw, 416px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><em>Look at Nextdoor‚Äôs happy, informative Highlights!</em></p>
<p>It‚Äôs no wonder why. Story Highlights are a fun way to make your Instagram profile more engaging while giving some of your best Story content a new life.</p>
<p>In this post, we‚Äôll share how you can use Instagram Highlights to promote your business and engage with customers. Now, let‚Äôs start by exploring what this feature is and how to use it, and then we‚Äôll dive into nine ways you can use it for your business!</p>
<h3>Table of contents</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="#what-are-instagram-highlights">What are Instagram Highlights?</a></li>
